  <main>
    <section class="page-header">
      <div class="container">
        <h1>How It Works</h1>
        <p>A simple, stress-free process for getting beautiful photos of your pets</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="content">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="steps">
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-number">1</div>
            <h3>Contact & Consultation</h3>
            <p>Reach out to discuss your vision and your pet's personality. We'll talk about locations, timing, and any special requests you have.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-number">2</div>
            <h3>Schedule Your Session</h3>
            <p>Pick a date and time that works best for you and your furry friend. We recommend early morning or late afternoon for the best natural lighting.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-number">3</div>
            <h3>The Photoshoot</h3>
            <p>Relax while we capture candid moments and posed shots of your pet. We work at your pet's pace to ensure they're comfortable and happy.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-number">4</div>
            <h3>Post-Processing & Delivery</h3>
            <p>We professionally edit your photos and deliver a beautiful collection within two weeks. You'll receive high-resolution digital files.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

